doctype html
html
    head
        title About Us - Quick Sale Savers
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css")
    body
        include navbar
        .container
            header
                h1 About Us
                p Discover who we are and what we stand for.

            .hero
                img(src="/banner.jpg" alt="About Us Image")
                .hero-text
                    h2 Our Mission
                    p At Quick Sale Savers, we are passionate about reducing waste and helping you save money. Our goal is to connect customers with ready-to-expire products at discounted prices, fostering sustainability and affordability.

            section.story
                h2 Our Story
                p Quick Sale Savers began with a simple idea: to tackle food waste while making shopping more economical. What started as a local initiative has now grown into a trusted platform helping customers and retailers across the region.

            section.values
                h2 Our Core Values
                .value-cards
                    .card
                        img(src="/sustainability.jpg" alt="Sustainability")
                        h3 Sustainability
                        p We aim to reduce waste and protect the environment by encouraging conscious consumption.
                    .card
                        img(src="/afford.png" alt="Affordability")
                        h3 Affordability
                        p Making shopping more accessible by offering unbeatable discounts on quality products.
                    .card
                        img(src="/community.jpg" alt="Community")
                        h3 Community
                        p Building a network of customers and retailers who care about the planet and each other.

            section.team
                h2 Meet Our Team
                .team-cards
                    .team-member
                        img(src="/user1.jpg" alt="Team Member 1")
                        h3 Jane Doe
                        p Founder & CEO
                    .team-member
                        img(src="/user2.jpg" alt="Team Member 2")
                        h3 John Smith
                        p Head of Operations
                    .team-member
                        img(src="/user3.jpg" alt="Team Member 3")
                        h3 Sarah Lee
                        p Marketing Lead

            footer
                p Â© 2024 Quick Sale Savers. All rights reserved.
